        statistics_name         |                                         exprs                                         |    n_distinct    
--------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+------------------
 documents_rum_index_6402_stats | {"bson_stats_project(document, 'b'::text)","bson_stats_project(document, 'c'::text)"} | {"-1, -2": 1000}
(1 row)

